scenes.description: Gura continues reading fan messages and looking at fan art from the book.
Gura transitions to talking about a 'goody bag' for the viewers.
Gura reveals and shows new emotes designed by Maerie.
Gura announces a surprise: a fully animated anime opening sequence (OP) for herself.
